{
"title":"Sweet Alert 插件",
"type":256,
"time":"2016/12/14 9:35",
"content":"<p>Sweet Alert 插件是一个不错弹出框插件。使用首先引入文件。</p><pre class='code'><span class='arrow'><</span><span class='tag'>script</span> <span class='attr'>src=</span><span class='str'>\"sweetalert.min.js\"</span><span class='arrow'>><</span><span class='arrow'>/</span><span class='tag'>script</span><span class='arrow'>></span><br><span class='arrow'><</span><span class='tag'>link</span> <span class='attr'>rel=</span><span class='str'>\"stylesheet\"</span> <span class='attr'>href=</span><span class='str'>\"sweetalert.css\"</span></pre><p>引入完成后，就可以在 JS 中定义使用了。</p><pre class='code'><span class='method'>swal</span><span class='word'>(</span><span class='flower'>{</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>title</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'标题'</span><span class='word'>,</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>text</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'文本'</span><span class='word'>,</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>type</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'warning'</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//可用的 type 有：warning、success、info、input、error</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>showCancelButton</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='key'>true</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 是否显示取消按钮，默认为 false</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>closeOnConfirm</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='key'>false</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 点击确定关闭，默认是 true</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>confirmButtonText</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'确认'</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 确定按钮文本内容，默认是 ok</span><span class='word'>,</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>confirmButtonColor</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'#ec6c62'</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>// 确定按钮的颜色，默认是一种有点蓝的颜色</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>animation</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'slide-from-top'</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;// 模态框出现的方式</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>imageUR</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'../url.png'</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 图片内容地址</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>html</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'直接写 HTML 内容'</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 直接写 HTML 可以显示在模态框内</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>allowOutsideClick</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='key'>false</span><span class='com'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 是否支持外部点击关闭，默认是 true</span><br><span class='flower'>}</span><span class='word'>,</span><span class='key'>function</span><span class='word'>()</span><span class='flower'>{</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='com'>/* 回调函数 */</span><br><span class='flower'>}</span><span class='word'>);</span></pre><p>在新版的 Sweet Alert2 中对回调函数做了一定的优化。上面写法的回调函数仅能对点击确定按钮生效。若要对点击取消做回调函数需要采用下面的写法：</p><pre class='code'><span class='method'>swal</span><span class='word'>(</span><span class='flower'>{</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>title</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='str'>'标题'</span><span class='word'>,</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='fun'>showCancelButton</span><span class='word'>:</span><span class='key'>true</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='com'>/* 其他参数略 */</span><br><span class='flower'>}</span><span class='word'>).</span><span class='method'>then</span><span class='word'>(</span><span class='key'>function</span><span class='word'>(isConfirm)</span><span class='flower'>{</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='key'>if</span><span class='word'>(isConfirm</span> <span class='key'>===</span> <span class='key'>true</span><span class='word'>)</span><span class='flower'>{</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='com'>/* 点击确定按钮后的回调操作 */</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='flower'>}</span><span class='key'>else</span><span class='flower'>{</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='com'>/* 点击取消按钮后的操作 */</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class='flower'>}</span><br><span class='flower'>}</span><span class='word'>);</span><span class=''></span></pre>"
}